import { Navigate } from 'react-router-dom'
import { PERMISSIONS_SECTIONS as permissions } from '../common/hooks/useUserPermission'
import Forgetpassword from '../pages/Authentication/forgetpassword'
import Signin from '../pages/Authentication/login'
import Logout from '../pages/Authentication/logout'
import Register from '../pages/Authentication/register'

const authProtectedRoutes = [
  {
    path: '/',
    exact: true,
    component: <Navigate to="/home" />,
    permissions: [permissions.home],
  },
  //HOME path
  { path: '/home', component: <Home />, permissions: [permissions.home] },
  { path: '/home', component: <Navigate to="/home" />, permissions: [permissions.home] },
]

const publicRoutes = [
  // Authentication
  { path: '/login', component: <Signin /> },
  { path: '/logout', component: <Logout /> },
  { path: '/register', component: <Register /> },
  { path: '/forgot-password', component: <Forgetpassword /> },
]

export { authProtectedRoutes, publicRoutes }
